        Property Valuations in Queensland: A Seller's Guide
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        An agent appraisal and a formal valuation are not the same thing. Queensland sellers need to understand when each applies, who can legally provide a valuation, and what happens when a buyer's bank disagrees with the sale price.
      </p>
